<HEAD>American, Three Britons Charged With Importing Drugs</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TRURO, England (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   An American and three Britons appeared in
court Saturday on charges they illegally imported $7.8 million
worth of marijuana.
   A special court in Truro, Cornwall in southeast England ordered
